<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Register Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .reg-success {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .reg-success span {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #4caf50;
        }
        .reg-success p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #7ff785;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="reg-success">
        <span>&check;</span>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. We have sent you an activation link. Please check your email and click on the link to verify your account.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
